<h2 name="requirements">Requirements :</h2>

<div class="doc2">
	<ul>
		<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/">Node.js</a> is a Platform built on Chrome's JavaScript runtime<p>Install Node.js <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager"> via Package</a></p></li>
		<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/">NPM</a> is the Package Manager for javascript application</li>
		<li><a href="http://git-scm.com/">GIT</a> is Distributed version control system</li>
		<li><a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/make/">GNU Make</a> is a Tool which controls the generation of executables</li>



	</ul>
</div>

